            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "It seems that it affects **only** pure python version. Cython alternatives works fine.\n\nEDIT: The issue is that pure python calls `get_view_utility_code()` even the memoryview code should not be loaded...\n\nhttps://github.com/cython/cython/blob/e311750b4afbdf4927a1e6476d27c14b2c492dd6/Cython/Compiler/MemoryView.py#L918",
