            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "OK here is the reproducer:\n\n```python\nimport cython\n\n@cython.cfunc\ndef main(a: cython.pointer[int]):\n    pass\n```\n\nCompiling it with `--shared=...` will produce following C code:\n\n```c\n/* \"meh.pxd\":76\n * cdef memoryview_cwrapper(object o, int flags, bint dtype_is_object, const __Pyx_TypeInfo *typeinfo)\n *\n * @cname('__pyx_memoryview_check')             # <<<<<<<<<<<<<<\n * cdef inline bint memoryview_check(object o) noexcept:\n *     return isinstance(o, memoryview)\n*/\n\nstatic CYTHON_INLINE int __pyx_memoryview_check(PyObject *__pyx_v_o) {\n  int __pyx_r;\n  int __pyx_t_1;\n\n  /* \"meh.pxd\":78\n * @cname('__pyx_memoryview_check')\n * cdef inline bint memoryview_check(object o) noexcept:\n *     return isinstance(o, memoryview)             # <<<<<<<<<<<<<<\n *\n * @cname('__pyx_memoryview_slice_memviewslice')\n*/\n  __pyx_t_1 = __Pyx_TypeCheck(__pyx_v_o, __pyx_mstate_global->__pyx_memoryview_type);\n  __pyx_r = __pyx_t_1;\n  goto __pyx_L0;\n\n  /* \"meh.pxd\":76\n * cdef memoryview_cwrapper(object o, int flags, bint dtype_is_object, const __Pyx_TypeInfo *typeinfo)\n *\n * @cname('__pyx_memoryview_check')             # <<<<<<<<<<<<<<\n * cdef inline bint memoryview_check(object o) noexcept:\n *     return isinstance(o, memoryview)\n*/\n\n  /* function exit code */\n  __pyx_L0:;\n  return __pyx_r;\n}\n```\n\nWhat is clearly wrong, The cause is that `cython.pointer[...]` type causes to call `MemoryView::get_view_utility_code()` with this stack:\n\n```\n-> modifiers, arg_type = annotation.analyse_type_annotation(env, assigned_value=self.default)\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ExprNodes.py(15460)analyse_type_annotation()\n-> modifiers = annotation.analyse_pytyping_modifiers(env) if annotation.is_subscript or isinstance(annotation, BitwiseOrNode) else []\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ExprNodes.py(4189)analyse_pytyping_modifiers()\n-> modifier_type = modifier_node.base.analyse_as_type(env)\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/ExprNodes.py(7964)analyse_as_type()\n-> return module_scope.lookup_type(self.attribute)\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/CythonScope.py(49)lookup_type()\n-> return super().lookup_type(name)\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/Symtab.py(1140)lookup_type()\n-> entry = self.lookup(name)\n  /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/CythonScope.py(55)lookup()\n-> self.load_cythonscope()\n> /home/dev/cython/Cython/Compiler/CythonScope.py(136)load_cythonscope()\n```",
